00:35:33,592 --> 00:35:35,761
Odavde do Nuova Larede...

219
00:35:35,969 --> 00:35:40,140
...nema restorana gde mogu da svrate.

220
00:35:40,307 --> 00:35:45,896
Svaki bandit ce ih traziti.

221
00:35:47,523 --> 00:35:52,653
Trazicu ih dok sam ziv.

222
00:35:53,862 --> 00:35:56,698
Mrtvi su, Dzek.
-Da ih nisi pipnuo.

223
00:35:57,366 --> 00:36:02,955
Kad mora da bude ovako, bokseru.
-Tako smo uradili.

224
00:36:06,708 --> 00:36:08,961
Secas se?

225
00:40:24,132 --> 00:40:26,927
Isao je koliko je brze mogao...

226
00:40:27,135 --> 00:40:32,516
dok ga nije izresetalo stotine dobrih strelaca...

227
00:40:32,724 --> 00:40:37,020
...licio je na izresetano sito.

228
00:40:37,688 --> 00:40:39,606
Kad bih samo mogao da biram...

229
00:40:42,109 --> 00:40:44,319
Drzeci se podalje
Marijetine mafije...

230
00:40:44,486 --> 00:40:46,738
...Dzek je da Hariju i Marijani
vremena da pobegnu...

231
00:40:46,905 --> 00:40:50,784
...Ukradeni novac je konacno
nasao put do pobunjenika.

232
00:40:50,951 --> 00:40:54,830
Jer je nagrada za greh-smrt.
Rimljani 4:23.

